=== Formula One ===
* [[Formula One World Drivers' Championship]] runner-up: {{F1|2022}}
* [[FIA Pole Trophy]]: 2019{{efn|The ''FIA Pole Trophy'' was only awarded from {{F1|2014}} to {{F1|2019}}. Leclerc also achieved the [[List of Formula One polesitters#Most pole positions per season|most pole positions]] in {{F1|2022}}.<ref name="FIA19">{{Cite web |url=https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article/leclerc-clinches-2019-pole-position-prize-despite-being-fourth-fastest.1PAwoZShgPbqODUEO2dp2D |title=Leclerc clinches 2019 pole position prize – despite being fourth fastest |date=16 November 2019 |website=[[Formula 1]] |publisher=[[Formula One Group]] |access-date=20 January 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250112142222/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article/leclerc-clinches-2019-pole-position-prize-despite-being-fourth-fastest.1PAwoZShgPbqODUEO2dp2D |archive-date=12 January 2025 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="2022analysis"/>}}
* [[FIA Prize Giving Ceremony#Rookie of the Year|FIA Rookie of the Year]]: 2018<ref name="FIA18">{{Cite magazine |url=https://racer.com/2018/12/08/hamilton-mercedes-leclerc-scoop-awards-at-fia-prize-giving-gala/ |title=Hamilton, Mercedes, Leclerc scoop awards at FIA prize-giving gala |date=8 December 2018 |magazine=[[Racer (magazine)|Racer]] |publisher=[[Racer (magazine)|Racer Media & Marketing Inc.]] |access-date=13 February 2025 |issn=1066-6060 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20241210040541/https://racer.com/2018/12/08/hamilton-mercedes-leclerc-scoop-awards-at-fia-prize-giving-gala/ |archive-date=10 December 2024 |url-status=live}}</ref>
* [[Lorenzo Bandini Trophy]]: 2020<ref name="LBT">{{Cite web |url=https://www.ferrari.com/en-EN/formula1/articles/ferrari-feted-at-the-trofeo-bandini |title=Ferrari feted at the Trofeo Bandini |date=13 July 2021 |website=[[Scuderia Ferrari]] |publisher=[[Ferrari]] |access-date=13 February 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20241108153124/https://www.ferrari.com/en-EN/formula1/articles/ferrari-feted-at-the-trofeo-bandini |archive-date=8 November 2024 |url-status=live}}</ref>
* [[Overtake Award]]: 2023<ref name="OA23">{{Cite web |url=https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article/crypto-com-overtake-of-the-month-award.4NSk8Aciia1hOZ9QEmmSjq |title=Crypto.com Overtake of the Year Award |date=15 December 2023 |website=[[Formula 1]] |publisher=[[Formula One Group]] |access-date=21 December 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250128152640/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article/crypto-com-overtake-of-the-month-award.4NSk8Aciia1hOZ9QEmmSjq |archive-date=28 January 2025 |url-status=live}}</ref>

